      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warming Persian-style lean beef & lentil stew</strong> over the<strong> cooked rice</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch out for any cardamom pods!</p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta</strong> over the top and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
